About this property

Comfortable Accommodations: Stadscamping Overboord in Den Bosch offers comfortable camping with free on-site private parking. Each unit includes a kitchen, dining area, and private bathroom. Modern Amenities: Guests enjoy air-conditioning, a refrigerator, and a seating area. Additional amenities include a barbecue, outdoor dining area, and free toiletries. Local Attractions: Located 21 mi from Eindhoven Airport, the camping is near Brabanthallen Exhibition Center (2.8 mi), De Efteling (17 mi), and other attractions. Outdoor Activities: Guests can enjoy kayaking or canoeing in the surrounding area.

How does it work?

    It starts with a booking

    Followed by a trip

    When guests stay at the property, they check out how quiet the room is, how friendly the staff is, and more.

  • 3

    And finally, a review
